        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses sleep movements of <hi rend="italic">Porlieria</hi>.</p>  
<p>Has read an abstract of Julius Wiesner on heliotropism and geotropism ["Die heliotropischen Erscheinungen im Pflanzenreiche", <hi rend="italic">Anz. Kais. Akad. Wiss. Wien</hi> 15 (1878): 137–40] which seems important but is puzzling.</p> 
            <p>Gives details of his observations on climbing plants with reference to comments by Julius Sachs.</p>
        </abstract>
